query:
update users 
            set 
            name = $1, 
            admin = $2, 
            address = $3, 
            phone = $4, 
            email = $5, 
            rate_hourly_cents = $6, 
            rate_mileage_cents = $7, 
            rate_drive_hourly_cents = $8,
            flat_rate_cents = $9
            where id = $10;
